content: As an AI language model, I don't have the ability to know for certain what voice actors think or feel. However, based on interviews and statements made by voice actors, it seems that many do have favorite characters they enjoy portraying. Some may have a personal connection to a particular character or enjoy the challenge of portraying a specific personality or vocal style. However, at the end of the day, voice acting is a job and professionals strive to do their best work for each and every project they are hired for.
